<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" identifier="Q12_v9" title="Q12_v9" time-dependent="false" adaptive="false" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceB</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="FEEDBACK" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SOLUTION" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float">
    <qti-default-value>
      <qti-value>0</qti-value>
    </qti-default-value>
  </qti-outcome-declaration>
  <qti-item-body>
    <p>Se muestra la siguiente factura abreviada:</p>
    <p>
      Factura de servicio:<br />
      - Valor del servicio (antes de impuesto): $<m:math><m:mn>80&#160;000</m:mn></m:math><br />
      - Impuesto aplicado: <m:math><m:mn>15</m:mn><m:mo>%</m:mo></m:math> del valor del servicio<br />
      - Total a pagar: valor del servicio + impuesto
    </p>
    <p>
      ¿Cuál es el monto del impuesto?
    </p>
    <qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" shuffle="false" max-choices="1">
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA">
        $<m:math><m:mn>8000</m:mn></m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceA" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">
          Incorrecto. El impuesto corresponde a 
          <m:math><m:mn>15</m:mn><m:mo>%</m:mo></m:math>
          de 
          <m:math><m:mn>80&#160;000</m:mn></m:math>.
          Primero, 
          <m:math><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mo>%</m:mo></m:math>
          de 
          <m:math><m:mn>80&#160;000</m:mn></m:math>
          es 
          <m:math><m:mn>8000</m:mn></m:math>
          y 
          <m:math><m:mn>5</m:mn><m:mo>%</m:mo></m:math>
          de 
          <m:math><m:mn>80&#160;000</m:mn></m:math>
          es 
          <m:math><m:mn>4000</m:mn></m:math>.
          Entonces,
          <m:math>
            <m:mrow>
              <m:mn>15</m:mn>
              <m:mo>%</m:mo>
              <m:mtext> = </m:mtext>
              <m:mn>10</m:mn>
              <m:mo>%</m:mo>
              <m:mtext> + </m:mtext>
              <m:mn>5</m:mn>
              <m:mo>%</m:mo>
            </m:mrow>
          </m:math>
          y
          <m:math>
            <m:mrow>
              <m:mn>8000</m:mn>
              <m:mo>+</m:mo>
              <m:mn>4000</m:mn>
              <m:mo>=</m:mo>
              <m:mn>12&#160;000</m:mn>
            </m:mrow>
          </m:math>.
          Por eso 
          <m:math><m:mn>8000</m:mn></m:math>
          no es el monto del impuesto.
        </qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB">
        $<m:math><m:mn>12&#160;000</m:mn></m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceB" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">
          ¡Correcto! El impuesto es 
          <m:math><m:mn>15</m:mn><m:mo>%</m:mo></m:math>
          de 
          <m:math><m:mn>80&#160;000</m:mn></m:math>.
          Como 
          <m:math><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mo>%</m:mo></m:math>
          de 
          <m:math><m:mn>80&#160;000</m:mn></m:math>
          es 
          <m:math><m:mn>8000</m:mn></m:math>
          y 
          <m:math><m:mn>5</m:mn><m:mo>%</m:mo></m:math>
          de 
          <m:math><m:mn>80&#160;000</m:mn></m:math>
          es 
          <m:math><m:mn>4000</m:mn></m:math>,
          al sumar se obtiene
          <m:math>
            <m:mrow>
              <m:mn>8000</m:mn>
              <m:mo>+</m:mo>
              <m:mn>4000</m:mn>
              <m:mo>=</m:mo>
              <m:mn>12&#160;000</m:mn>
            </m:mrow>
          </m:math>.
          Por lo tanto, el monto del impuesto es 
          <m:math><m:mn>12&#160;000</m:mn></m:math>.
        </qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC">
        $<m:math><m:mn>92&#160;000</m:mn></m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceC" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">
          Incorrecto. El impuesto es solo una parte del valor del servicio, no el total a pagar. 
          <m:math>
            <m:mrow>
              <m:mn>15</m:mn>
              <m:mo>%</m:mo>
              <m:mtext> de </m:mtext>
              <m:mn>80&#160;000</m:mn>
              <m:mo>=</m:mo>
              <m:mn>12&#160;000</m:mn>
            </m:mrow>
          </m:math>.
          En cambio,
          <m:math>
            <m:mrow>
              <m:mn>80&#160;000</m:mn>
              <m:mo>+</m:mo>
              <m:mn>12&#160;000</m:mn>
              <m:mo>=</m:mo>
              <m:mn>92&#160;000</m:mn>
            </m:mrow>
          </m:math>,
          que corresponde al total a pagar y no al impuesto.
        </qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD">
        $<m:math><m:mn>24&#160;000</m:mn></m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceD" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">
          Incorrecto. 
          <m:math>
            <m:mrow>
              <m:mn>15</m:mn>
              <m:mo>%</m:mo>
              <m:mtext> de </m:mtext>
              <m:mn>80&#160;000</m:mn>
              <m:mo>=</m:mo>
              <m:mn>12&#160;000</m:mn>
            </m:mrow>
          </m:math>,
          no 
          <m:math><m:mn>24&#160;000</m:mn></m:math>.
          De hecho, 
          <m:math><m:mn>24&#160;000</m:mn></m:math>
          corresponde a 
          <m:math><m:mn>30</m:mn><m:mo>%</m:mo></m:math>
          de 
          <m:math><m:mn>80&#160;000</m:mn></m:math>,
          porque 
          <m:math><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mo>%</m:mo></m:math>
          es 
          <m:math><m:mn>8000</m:mn></m:math>
          y
          <m:math>
            <m:mrow>
              <m:mn>30</m:mn>
              <m:mo>%</m:mo>
              <m:mtext> = </m:mtext>
              <m:mn>3</m:mn>
              <m:mo>·</m:mo>
              <m:mn>10</m:mn>
              <m:mo>%</m:mo>
            </m:mrow>
          </m:math>,
          es decir,
          <m:math>
            <m:mrow>
              <m:mn>3</m:mn>
              <m:mo>·</m:mo>
              <m:mn>8000</m:mn>
              <m:mo>=</m:mo>
              <m:mn>24&#160;000</m:mn>
            </m:mrow>
          </m:math>.
        </qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
    <qti-feedback-block identifier="show" outcome-identifier="SOLUTION" show-hide="show">
      <qti-content-body>
        <p><strong>Resolución paso a paso</strong></p>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 1: Identificar qué se pide</strong></p>
            <p>Se pide el monto del impuesto, no el total a pagar.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 2: Calcular el 10% del valor del servicio</strong></p>
            <p>El valor del servicio es $80 000.</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mn>10</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>%</m:mo>
                  <m:mtext> de </m:mtext>
                  <m:mn>80&#160;000</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>8000</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 3: Calcular el 5% del valor del servicio</strong></p>
            <p>Como 5% es la mitad de 10%, entonces:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mn>5</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>%</m:mo>
                  <m:mtext> de </m:mtext>
                  <m:mn>80&#160;000</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>4000</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 4: Sumar para obtener el 15%</strong></p>
            <p>Como 15% = 10% + 5%, se suma:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mn>8000</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>4000</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>12&#160;000</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Conclusión</strong></p>
            <p>El monto del impuesto es $12 000, por lo tanto la alternativa correcta es la B.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Verificación del total a pagar</strong></p>
            <p>Si se quisiera calcular el total, entonces:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mn>80&#160;000</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>12&#160;000</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>92&#160;000</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
            <p>Esto confirma que $92 000 es el total a pagar, no el impuesto.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </qti-content-body>
    </qti-feedback-block>
  </qti-item-body>
  <qti-response-processing>
    <qti-response-condition>
      <qti-response-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SCORE">
          <qti-base-value base-type="float">1</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else>
    </qti-response-condition>
  </qti-response-processing>
</qti-assessment-item>